msgid "Spiritual Seekers and Mystics"
msgstr "Vatsvagiri Veupenyu HweMwari uye vanamazvikokota"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Curious, introspective, open-minded, and drawn to "
"esoteric knowledge. They may have a strong interest in uncovering hidden "
"meanings or patterns in life. Occupations: Spiritual coaches, tarot readers,"
" astrologers, or individuals involved in New Age practices. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to lean toward spiritual or metaphysical beliefs. They may "
"see the tools as a way to connect with deeper truths or universal energies."
msgstr ""
"Zvivakwa zvehunhu: Kuziva, kuongorora, kusiri kwechinyakare, uye kunzwisisa "
"ruzivo rwemukati. Vanogona kuva nechido chikuru chekutsvaga zvisiri pachena "
"kana maonero muupenyu. Mabasa: Vadzidzisi veupenyu hweMwari, vanoona tarot, "
"vanoona zvingaitwa nemhepo, kana vanhu vanobatanidzwa nehutano hwe New Age. "
"Zvigadzirwa zvepfungwa: Zvinotarisirwa kuve nechido chekuziva kweupenyu "
"hweMwari kana pfungwa dze metafiziki. Vanogona kuona michina seyambiro "
"yekubatana ne chokwadi chiri pasi kana simba reupenyu."

msgid "Numerologists and Gematria Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Vanoongorora manhamba neVanofarira Gematria"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Analytical, detail-oriented, and fascinated by the "
"relationship between numbers and language. They may enjoy decoding symbolic "
"meanings. Occupations: Freelance numerologists, writers on esoteric topics, "
"or hobbyists exploring numerology. Ideological Spectrum: May range from "
"those who view numerology as a fun intellectual exercise to those who "
"believe in its profound spiritual significance."
msgstr ""
"Zvivakwa zvehunhu: Kuongorora, kutarisa zvakadzama, uye kufarira hukama "
"hwemanhamba nezvinyorwa. Vanogona kufarira kudzvanya pfungwa dzekodhi. "
"Mabasa: Vanoongorora manhamba vasina basa, vanyori pane zvemukati, kana "
"vanofarira kuongorora manhamba. Zvigadzirwa zvepfungwa: Zvinogona "
"kusanganisira vanhu vanotenda manhamba sechiitiko chinonakidza, kana "
"vanotenda kukosha kweupenyu hweMwari."

msgid "Historians and Linguists"
msgstr "Vanhoroondo neVanyora"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Scholarly, methodical, and interested in historical or "
"cultural contexts of numerical systems like Abjad. Occupations: Academics, "
"researchers, or students studying Middle Eastern languages, history, or "
"religious texts. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools from a "
"secular, academic perspective, focusing on their historical or linguistic "
"significance."
msgstr ""
"Zvivakwa zvehunhu: Vanokudzwa, vanoshanda nekuronga, uye vanofarira "
"zvinyorwa zvemazuva ano kana zvetsika zvepamusoro pemaitiro semuenzaniso "
"Abjad. Mabasa: Vanyanzvi, vanoshandira, kana vadzidzi vanodzidza mitauro ye "
"Middle Eastern, nhoroondo, kana mafaera ezvitendero. Zvigadzirwa zvepfungwa:"
" Zvinowanzo tarisira michina sechigadzirwa chepamusoro, zvichibatanidzwa "
"nezvidzidzo, uchitsvaka kukosha kwavo kwechinyorwa kana tsika."

msgid "Religious or Faith-Based Individuals"
msgstr "Vanhu Vekutenda kana Vechitendero"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Devout, reflective, and seeking deeper connections to "
"their faith. They may use the tools to explore religious texts or divine "
"messages. Occupations: Religious scholars, imams, priests, or laypeople with"
" a strong interest in their faith’s mystical traditions. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to have a traditional or conservative worldview, using the "
"tools to reinforce their spiritual beliefs."
msgstr ""
"Zvivakwa zvehunhu: Vakarurama, vanofungisisa, uye vanotsvaga kubatana "
"kwakadzika nechiitiko chavo. Vanogona kushandisa michina yekutarisa mafaera "
"ezvitendero kana mashoko anobva kuna Mwari. Mabasa: Vanyanzvi vepamusoro, "
"imams, vatongi, kana vanhu vakasvibira vane chido chetsika dzemusoro "
"dzakadzama. Zvigadzirwa zvepfungwa: Zvinowanzo kukoshesa maonero emazuva ano"
" kana zvinyorwa, kushandisa michina kuisa pfungwa dzavo dzesungano."

msgid "Writers and Artists"
msgstr "Vanyori neVanyori"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Creative, imaginative, and drawn to symbolic or abstract"
" concepts. They may use the tools for inspiration or to add layers of "
"meaning to their work. Occupations: Authors, poets, visual artists, or "
"musicians. Ideological Spectrum: May range from secular creatives to those "
"with a spiritual or mystical bent."
msgstr ""
"Zvivakwa zvehunhu: Kugadzira, kufunga, uye kuenderana nepfungwa dzekumashure"
" kana dzekumashure. Vanogona kushandisa michina sechirevo kana kuwedzera "
"zvakawanda zvezvinhu zvavo. Mabasa: Vanyori, maipo, vashandisi, kana "
"vatambi. Zvigadzirwa zvepfungwa: Zvinogona kusanganisira vashandi "
"vanodzidzira, kana vanhu vanofungidzira."

msgid "Puzzle and Riddle Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Vatsvagiri VePuzzle neMibvunzo"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Playful, intellectually curious, and enjoy solving "
"complex problems or decoding patterns. Occupations: Hobbyists, puzzle "
"designers, or educators. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools "
"as a form of entertainment or mental exercise, with little ideological "
"attachment."
msgstr ""
"Zvivakwa zvehunhu: Kutamba, kufunga kwepfungwa, uye kufarira kugadzirisa "
"matambudziko akaomarara kana kudzvanya maitiro. Mabasa: Vatsva, vanogadzira "
"puzzles, kana varairidzi. Zvigadzirwa zvepfungwa: Zvinowanzo kuwana michina "
"sechirongwa chekunakidzwa kana kufungira, pasina kutenderera kwakadzama."

msgid "Conspiracy Theorists and Alternative Thinkers"
msgstr "Vatarisi veMambo uye Vafunga Vakasiyana"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to uncovering "
"hidden truths or patterns in systems. Occupations: Independent researchers, "
"bloggers, or activists. Ideological Spectrum: May have a more radical or "
"unconventional worldview, using the tools to support alternative theories or"
" narratives."
msgstr ""
"Zvivakwa zvehunhu: Vanokakavara nezvinyorwa zvechokwadi, vanobva kuvakirwa "
"kukanganisa zvisiri pachena kana maitiro muzvivako. Mabasa: Vatsva, "
"vashandi, kana varairidzi. Zvigadzirwa zvepfungwa: Zvinogona kusanganisira "
"vatambi vanoda kufungira, kana vanofungidzira zvakasiyana."

